		<h1>We now support messaging offline users!</h1>
		<p>No longer will you need to wait for your friends to come online to talk to them! It's been requested for years, and after a lot of work, I've introduced offline messaging! Simply chat in the PM window like you normally would, and after a quick confirmation the message will be off, to be received by the target user when they log back in. For more information, see <a href="https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/3650958/post-9855640" target="_blank">this post.</a></p>		<p>
